                <h1 class="pure-u-1">Kiln</h1>
                <h2 class="pure-u-3-4">
                    Kiln is a multi-platform framework for building and deploying complex
                    websites whose source content is primarily in XML. It brings together
                    various independent software components into an integrated whole that
                    provides the infrastructure and base functionality for such sites.
                </h2>

